                            </div>
                            <h4 style="color: @headingColor; font-size: 1.5em; margin: 0;">Platinum insurance partner</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p style="color: @mainTextColor; font-size: 1.05em; line-height: 1.6;">PrimeProtect is one of the largest partners for most health insurance companies. Our dedicated claims team works with the insurance companies to help you answer insurer queries and track your claim settlement.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row justify-content-center" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-6" style="flex: 0 0 auto; width: 41.666667%; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                    <div class="feature-card" style="background-color: @cardBgColor; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border: 1px solid @borderColor; height: 100%;">
                        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                            <div class="card-icon-wrapper" style="background-color: @accentColor; color: @buttonTextColor; border-radius: 50%; width: 50px; height: 50px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-size: 1.5em; margin-right: 15px;">
                                <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                            </div>
